OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, cloud
OL,6,Fwill increase from the south to bring
OL,7,Fsome outbreaks of showery rain during
OL,8,Fthe morning. Locally heavy afternoon
OL,9,Fshowers in the west, eastern areas
OL,10,Fdrier.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers will ease into the
OL,13,Fevening, the cloud will break
OL,14,Fovernight with light winds,
OL,15,Ftemperatures will fall with mist and
OL,16,Ffog patches readily forming. Feeling
OL,17,Fcold.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
