OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FWarm bright spells and dry
OL,6,Fduring the day. Cloudy overnight and
OL,7,Fbecoming breezy with the chance of
OL,8,Fsome showers in the south.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,11,Fnarrow band of rain moves south on
OL,12,FSunday, with brighter skies following.
OL,13,FSome showers Monday. Often breezy and
OL,14,Ffeeling cooler. Tuesday sunny at first
OL,15,Fthen cloudy with showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
